text: Elizabeth Bay may refer to: *Elizabeth Bay, New South Wales, a harbourside suburb in eastern Sydney, New South Wales, Australia *Elisabeth Bay, Isabela Island (Ecuador), a natural bay on the coast of Isabela Island, Galapagos. *Elizabeth Bay, Namibia (formerly Elisabethbucht) is a ghost town in southern Namibia. ==See also== *Elizabeth Bay House, a historic home in the suburb of Elizabeth Bay, Sydney Australia.
title: Elizabeth Bay
